name: Crypt of the Jeweled King - Crystallization of Memories
description: He lays in his glass coffin, content, adorned with all his jewels for eternity. I guess you CAN take them with you. It might seem superficial, but each jewel was once a moment in time, that added on to who he was and what he would become and how the next journey would go. They simply looked like memories until the crystallization of the passing thru dimensions.
